RESOURCE.DESCRIPTION: Helio HEC time based query V1.16.25
RESOURCE.INFO: SELECT wind_mfi_mag_cloud.HEC_id,wind_mfi_mag_cloud.time_start,wind_mfi_mag_cloud.time_end,wind_mfi_mag_cloud.code,wind_mfi_mag_cloud.quality FROM wind_mfi_mag_cloud WHERE time_start>='2003-02-01T00:00:00' AND time_start<='2003-02-10T00:00:00' LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

FIELD.name: time_start
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated start time of magnetic cloud (using the magnetic field model of Lepping et al., 1990). .

FIELD.name: time_end
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated end time of the magnetic cloud (using the magnetic field model of Lepping et al., 1990).
